name: Witches of East End
overview: The adventures of Joanna Beauchamp and her two adult daughters Freya and Ingrid -- both of whom unknowingly are their family's next generation of witches -- who lead seemingly quiet, uneventful modern day lives in Long Island's secluded seaside town of East Haven. When Freya becomes engaged to a young, wealthy newcomer, a series of events forces Joanna to admit to her daughters they are, in fact, powerful and immortal witches.

episodes.name: Pilot
episodes.overview: Joanna Beauchamp and her adult daughters Ingrid and Freya are witches… a secret she has kept hidden from them for the last thirty years. All that may come to an abrupt end when Joanna’s sister Wendy returns to East Haven with a dire warning that a powerful and malevolent force bent on revenge is coming for Joanna, and it will take the combined magic of all the Beauchamp women to defeat it.

episodes.name: Marilyn Fenwick, R.I.P.
episodes.overview: Ingrid discovers mysterious and dangerous family heirlooms that she uses to resurrect her Aunt Wendy. Together, they race to save Freya from Doug, her jilted ex-boyfriend from another lifetime. Joanna is jailed and questioned by the police regarding her murder charge. Dash and Killian have a tense reunion.

episodes.name: Today I Am a Witch
episodes.overview: Ingrid struggles with the consequences of the resurrection spell. Joanna tries to figure out which of her many former enemies might be responsible for framing her. Wendy teaches Ingrid and Freya how to use their powers. Freya gets a new co-worker at the bar.

episodes.name: A Few Good Talismen
episodes.overview: Joanna's immortal attorney, Harrison, prepares for her murder trial. Afraid for Adam's safety, Ingrid re-evaluates her relationship with him. Penelope recruits Freya to help her mend the rift between Dash and Killian. Wendy seduces an entomologist while trying to gather ingredients for a spell. And Joanna and Harrison try to protect Principal Redmond from the shifter.

episodes.name: Electric Avenue
episodes.overview: Ingrid finds a unique way to mourn for Adam. Joanna and Harrison take their friendship to the next level. Freya meets Dash's ex fiancée Elyse when she returns to deal with some unfinished business.

episodes.name: Potentia Noctis
episodes.overview: Freya makes a startling discovery at Fair Haven while Ingrid has flashbacks to one of her past lives.

episodes.name: Unburied
episodes.overview: The shifter summons a familiar face. Ingrid discovers something startling from her past. A novelist comes to East End to research his new book. Wendy turns over a new leaf, and attempts to get serious with Leo. Joanna reads Freya's tarot cards.

episodes.name: Snake Eyes
episodes.overview: Wendy and Joanna come to blows over a secret Joanna has been keeping for over a hundred years. The shifter threatens Freya. Ingrid suspects Mike's ulterior motives.

episodes.name: A Parching Imbued
episodes.overview: A mysterious professor with old connections to the Beauchamps tries to help Freya regain her powers. Killian makes a decision about his future in East End. Mike reveals an interesting theory to Ingrid. Amidst wedding preparations, Dash tries to solve the mystery of the catacombs.

episodes.name: Oh, What a World!
episodes.overview: Freya's wedding day arrives as do gifts from both Killian and Dash. Joanna and Wendy discover the identity of the shifter. When Ingrid discovers some unnerving details about Mike, he takes dangerous measures to complete his plan.

episodes.name: A Moveable Beast
episodes.overview: All the Beauchamp witches have trouble remembering exactly what happened after the portal opened and fear a mystical presence crossed over to their world. Victor helps Joanna fight what seems to be a losing battle with her argentum poisoning. Ingrid develops a dangerous sleep walking habit while Freya has visions of Killian in danger.

episodes.name: The Son Also Rises
episodes.overview: Joanna is thrilled with Frederick’s return, while Wendy remains suspicious of his behavior. Killian discovers he has a lot in common with new love Eva. Dash reluctantly deals with his blackmailer.

episodes.name: The Old Man and the Key
episodes.overview: Ingrid prepares to move out while Freya tracks down Killian. Dash discovers the identity of his blackmailer and plans revenge. Wendy and Joanna follow Frederick to figure out what his motives are since reconnecting with the family.

episodes.name: The Brothers Grimoire
episodes.overview: Wendy and Tommy have a disastrous series of meetings. Old friends of Frederick’s from Asgard make an unwelcome visit to Fair Haven. Dash and Killian receive their inheritance which yields interesting results.

episodes.name: Boogie Knight
episodes.overview: Freya relives one of her past lives with Killian. Dash does a spell at work without realizing the consequences. Joanna seeks the help of an old friend, Alex. Wendy and Freddie work together to try and stop the Mandragora while Ingrid’s bond with it grows stronger.

episodes.name: When a Mandragora Loves a Woman
episodes.overview: Joanna and Alex must put their past aside and focus on finding the Mandragora. Freya asks Dash to help save Ingrid. Skeptical of Freddie’s loyalty, Wendy is wary of his actions.

episodes.name: Art of Darkness
episodes.overview: Tarkoff, an old friend of the family’s, pays a visit to Joanna and Freddie. Wendy, Freya, Ingrid and Dash attend an art gala where Wendy encounters someone from her past. Killian has doubts about his feelings for Eva.

episodes.name: Sex,Lies and Birthday Cake
episodes.overview: Joanna has to face up to one of her worst fears. It is a milestone birthday for Freya and Frederick. Wendy gives Tommy a surprise. Frederick is feeling the pressure from Tarkoff to get things done.

episodes.name: Smells Like King Spirit
episodes.overview: Tarkoff gains revenge on Frederick. Freya confronts Killian. Dash is issued with an ultimatum. Joanna tries to protect her family.

episodes.name: The Fall of the House of Beauchamp
episodes.overview: Dash's secrets begin to unravel; Joanna is devastated by Tarkoff's actions. Wendy and Joanna decide to reconnect with their father.

episodes.name: Poe Way Out
episodes.overview: Joanna, Freya and Wendy revisit one of their former lives. Dash's one night stand turns out to be somebody better than expected. Ingrid attempts to bond with her grandfather.

episodes.name: Box to the Future
episodes.overview: The Beauchamps travel back in time to the 1840s where Freya encounters Edgar Allan Poe and Joanna is ensnared by a dangerous admirer. Killian does the unthinkable and risks his life for his one true love.

episodes.name: For Whom the Spell Tolls
episodes.overview: Season two ends with Jonanna trying to escape from Tarkoff, while Freya and Wendy race to find a way back to the present. As far as Ingrid, she learned some shocking news about herself from King Nikolaus, and Dash's dark past closes in on him.
